description: Otovo ASA, together with its subsidiaries, operates an online marketplace for solar installations in Norway. It operates through two segments, Marketplace and Subscription SPV. The company develops and manages an online sales platform, which provides subscription for solar panel installations and related products for private households. It operates in Europe, Norway, Sweden, Poland, Italy, Germany, Switzerland, Austria, France, the Netherlands, Belgium, Spain, Portugal, and the United Kingdom. Otovo ASA was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Oslo, Norway.
